high_descs: turn and walk to face sink
pick up white mug from inside sink basin
walk to the left to fridge, turn to face fridge
open fridge door, put mug on shelf with glass bottles, close door, wait, open fridge door, pick up white mug, close fridge door
turn right, walk to face coffee maker to the left of the kitchen sink
put mug inside coffee maker on the counter top
anns.task_desc: chill a mug to put inside the coffee maker

high_descs: Take as step to the left to face the sink.
Pick up the white cup from the sink.
Turn left and walk towards the fridge to your right.
Place the cup on the top shelf in the fridge, let it cool, and take it back out.
Turn right and head towards the coffee maker on your left.
Place the cup on the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Cool down the cup from the sink as well as put it on the coffee maker.

high_descs: Take a step to the left to locate the sink.
Pick up the cup from the sink.
Carry the cup and take a few steps to the left to find the fridge.
Open the fridge door and place the cup inside. Shut the door, then open it and take out the cup. Shut the door.
Carry the cup and take a few steps to the right to locate the coffee maker.
Place the cup on the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Chill a cup and place it on the coffee maker.
